  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Fit For Emperors And Kings
---
Hu Tzu said, "Just now I appeared to him as Heaven and Earth - no name
or substance to it, but still the workings, coming up from the heels.
He probably saw in me the Workings of the Good One. Try bringing him
again."
